      \"check\":\"true\",
      \"skill_text\":\"When you [i]Face Danger[/i], [i]Secure an Advantage[/i], or [i]Compel[/i] by hitting or breaking an inanimate object, add +1 and take +1 momentum on a hit.\"
    }
  },
  
  {
    \"skill\" : {
      \"check\":\"false\",
      \"skill_text\":\"When you [i]Strike[/i] a foe to knock them back, stun them, or put them off balance, inflict 1 harm (instead of 2) and take +2 momentum on a hit. On a [b]strong hit[/b], you also create an opening and add +1 on your next move.\"
    }
  },
  
  {
    \"skill\" : {
      \"check\":\"false\",
      \"skill_text\":\"When you [i]Turn the Tide[/i], you may [i]Strike[/i] with all the fury and power you can muster. If you do (decide before rolling), you may reroll any dice and inflict +2 harm on a [b]strong hit[/b], but count a [b]weak hit[/b] as a miss.\"
    }
  }
  
]"
